docs.lead_paragraph: Not so long ago, Colorado's Republican Party relished the chance to unseat Democratic U.S. Sen. Michael Bennet in this presidential swing state. Now it's presiding over a primary featuring five second-tier candidates who are fighting just to make themselves known to deliver Bennet an opponent.

headline.main: 5 Colorado Republicans Fight to Take on Democrat Bennet
headline.print_headline: 5 Colorado Republicans Fight to Take on Democrat Bennet
